<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-error">MAY25 </span>=
<br>
 BUGFIX : To show clean incremental tiers in the UI, we need to increment t=
he n+1 start tier with .01.<br><br>
 So currently, tier[0].endRange =3D=3D tier[1].startRange.<br><br>
 What needs to be implemented is that for any tier except tier[0] the follo=
wing gets done:<br><br>
 1) parse tier[x].startRange as integer&nbsp;<br>
 2) increment (+) that integer with 0.01 <br>
 3) Overwrite the old startRange value with the new value from step 2.<br><=
br>
 This should make the tier array return like this:<br><strong><span style=
=3D"color: rgb(85,85,85);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(85,85,85);"><br></span=
></span></strong></p>
